org.prebake.core
Class Documentation

java.lang.Object
  org.prebake.core.Documentation
All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonSerializable
@ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public final class Documentation
extends java.lang.Object
implements JsonSerializable

Structured documentation of a system artifact.

When converted from JSON, the summary is inferred by looking at the first sentence. This class uses JavaDoc conventions for finding the first sentence instead of trying to segment human languages.

Method Detail

summaryOf

public static java.lang.String summaryOf(java.lang.String detailHtml)
Implements Javadoc's summary string convention. Per javadoc
This sentence ends at the first period that is followed by a blank, tab, or line terminator, or at the first tag (as defined below). For example, this first sentence ends at "Prof.":
This is a simulation of Prof. Knuth's MIX computer.
